00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:19,840
[Boys Over Flowers]

6
00:00:21,110 --> 00:00:23,620
[Episode 24]

7
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:31,100
There's something going on with you, isn't there?

8
00:00:33,594 --> 00:00:35,448
You're not sleeping?

9
00:00:35,448 --> 00:00:38,229
Don't even think about lying to me.

10
00:00:40,107 --> 00:00:42,626
There's nothing going on.

11
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:51,900
I want to live here with dad, you and San.

12
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:53,445
What?

13
00:00:54,139 --> 00:00:55,673
Why?

14
00:00:55,673 --> 00:01:00,093
What about Young Master Joon Pyo, school and everything?

15
00:01:00,093 --> 00:01:04,700
Didn't I say it before? I have nothing to do with Goo Joon Pyo.

16
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:09,070
Are you still thinking about it, even after going through all the humiliation?

17
00:01:09,070 --> 00:01:14,220
So, selling fish, crabs and webfoot octopus in this rural town,

18
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:16,880
and smelling of fish is how you want to live?

19
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,150
What's wrong with that?

20
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:25,560
We're ruined.

21
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,900
We're done for!

22
00:01:29,550 --> 00:01:32,900
What hope do we have to live for now?

23
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,630
What should we do...

24
00:01:40,798 --> 00:01:42,891
Mom.

25
00:01:42,891 --> 00:01:45,107
Forget it!

26
00:02:03,686 --> 00:02:05,931
Yi Jung Sunbae...

27
00:02:21,433 --> 00:02:25,729
There's still no news from Jan Di?

28
00:02:25,729 --> 00:02:29,515
No. I don't know what she's thinking.

29
00:02:29,515 --> 00:02:31,020
She hasn't called.

30
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:35,990
She just said she went to a fishing village but never said where it is.

31
00:02:35,990 --> 00:02:39,768
She must be doing ok. It's Geum Jan Di we're talking about.

32
00:02:41,128 --> 00:02:45,537
You seem to know my friends better than I do.

33
00:02:45,537 --> 00:02:49,251
Like I said before, I have some knowledge when it comes to girls.

34
00:02:53,689 --> 00:02:56,804
How is Joon Pyo doing?

35
00:02:56,804 --> 00:02:58,781
He's a mess.

36
00:03:02,657 --> 00:03:04,558
Ga Eul...

37
00:03:05,705 --> 00:03:09,683
Don't you think it's time we start talking about us?

38
00:03:21,095 --> 00:03:23,566
Ga Eul. I...

39
00:03:23,566 --> 00:03:26,014
I'll go first.

40
00:03:27,424 --> 00:03:31,360
You don't have to feel burdened because of me.

41
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:35,570
I already know how you feel.

42
00:03:36,247 --> 00:03:40,272
So, from now on, I won't look for you anymore.

43
00:03:40,272 --> 00:03:41,518
Ga Eul!

44
00:03:41,518 --> 00:03:44,760
Teacher, I mean...

45
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,450
Eun Jae teacher said before,

46
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:53,660
that because she did everything that was within her power, that she has no regrets.

47
00:03:55,638 --> 00:03:57,718
Thank you,

48
00:03:57,718 --> 00:04:00,966
for giving me the chance to do everything I could.

49
00:04:03,474 --> 00:04:06,702
If I hear from Jandi, I will inform you.
Bye.

50
00:04:06,702 --> 00:04:08,311
Bye.

51
00:05:18,935 --> 00:05:21,171
What can we do?

52
00:05:21,171 --> 00:05:27,170
Mister, I am so afraid that our Joon Pyo might break.

53
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:29,180
I'm really afraid.

54
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:32,020
Miss, you can't be like this too.

55
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:33,859
No.

56
00:05:33,859 --> 00:05:35,986
You see,

57
00:05:35,986 --> 00:05:38,629
I have a really bad feeling about this.

58
00:05:47,898 --> 00:05:49,548
Miss?

59
00:07:08,431 --> 00:07:12,935
Dad... Dad...

60
00:07:12,935 --> 00:07:14,773
Dad!

61
00:07:38,873 --> 00:07:41,662
How could you do this?

62
00:07:42,682 --> 00:07:46,596
Can't you see it's already hard without you screaming about it?

63
00:07:46,596 --> 00:07:48,530
Mom...

64
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:52,720
No, I don't even want to call you mom anymore.

65
00:07:53,724 --> 00:07:55,790
How...

66
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:58,510
How could a person...

67
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,534
How could someone do something like that?

68
00:08:00,534 --> 00:08:02,224
What exactly are you talking about?

69
00:08:02,224 --> 00:08:06,618
How could you say that dad was dead when he's still alive?!

70
00:08:08,205 --> 00:08:10,858
- You...
- How did I know?

71
00:08:10,858 --> 00:08:13,483
You're wondering about that at a time like this?

72
00:08:13,483 --> 00:08:15,130
I'm asking you.

73
00:08:15,130 --> 00:08:18,692
Leaving Dad buried like that, did you intend to deceive me forever?!

74
00:08:18,692 --> 00:08:21,798
Why did you do that?! Why?!

75
00:08:23,925 --> 00:08:26,676
This is what your father would have wanted.

76
00:08:26,676 --> 00:08:29,240
W... W... What?

77
00:08:30,647 --> 00:08:33,340
I said I would take care of everything,

78
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:35,680
but your dad suddenly collapsed.

79
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:39,140
He isn't different from a living corpse.

80
00:08:39,140 --> 00:08:41,880
The head of the famous Shinhwa Group...

81
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:45,690
I couldn't allow the last memories of him to become like that.

82
00:08:46,956 --> 00:08:50,082
My pride wouldn't allow it.

83
00:08:51,427 --> 00:08:54,160
Pride...

84
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:59,420
Now... You're saying you lied to the world and even to your children,

85
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:05,066
that my living father was dead due to pride?

86
00:09:06,096 --> 00:09:08,607
It was for your dad.

87
00:09:11,838 --> 00:09:13,796
What is this about?

88
00:09:18,089 --> 00:09:19,826
Joon Pyo...

89
00:09:20,663 --> 00:09:23,935
I'll explain everything. I...

90
00:09:23,935 --> 00:09:26,975
I'll explain everything. I...
I asked, what's going on?!

91
00:09:57,522 --> 00:10:01,006
When dad is not around, what do you have to do?

92
00:10:01,006 --> 00:10:05,593
I have to take care of mom, noona, and Shinhwa Group!

93
00:10:05,593 --> 00:10:09,583
Goo Joon Pyo, can you promise me that, man to man?

94
00:10:09,583 --> 00:10:11,635
Yes, sir!

95
00:10:11,635 --> 00:10:16,710
Your father tried his hardest 'til the very end for this group,

96
00:10:16,710 --> 00:10:20,800
which you can throw away any minute.

97
00:10:22,241 --> 00:10:24,676
Are you thinking of abandoning him as well?

98
00:10:33,848 --> 00:10:36,438
I'm sorry, Young Master.

99
00:10:36,438 --> 00:10:38,690
I am really sorry.

100
00:11:16,206 --> 00:11:19,360
This time, it was me who realized

101
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:24,530
that you and I were from two different worlds.

102
00:11:24,530 --> 00:11:29,041
As much as you try to deny it, you are still Shinhwa Group's Goo Joon Pyo.

103
00:11:29,041 --> 00:11:32,645
I haven't once forgotten that.

104
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:48,530
♫ Because I'm stupid ♫

105
00:11:48,530 --> 00:11:53,730
♫ I know no one but you ♫

106
00:11:53,730 --> 00:11:58,990
♫ But you are looking at someone else ♫

107
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:04,260
♫ You wouldn't know how I feel ♫

108
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:09,430
♫ I wouldn't be in your day ♫

109
00:12:09,430 --> 00:12:14,660
♫ I wouldn't even be in your memory ♫

110
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:19,740
♫ I still keep looking at you only ♫

111
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:25,890
♫ My tears keep rolling ♫

112
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:30,140
♫ Your backside ♫

113
00:12:30,140 --> 00:12:35,420
♫ Looking at that is also a happiness ♫

114
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:40,670
♫ If you still don't know how I feel ♫

115
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:47,800
♫ If I stop this and go too ♫

116
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:51,127
I came to the fish market today. Everyone, look at the fresh fish here.

117
00:12:51,127 --> 00:12:55,298
The stall is full of fish.

118
00:12:55,298 --> 00:12:58,170
- Look at this octopus.
- $10!

119
00:12:58,170 --> 00:13:00,444
- It seems this is the season for octopus.
- $10!

120
00:13:00,444 --> 00:13:04,130
Sure! It's drop-dead delicious!

121
00:13:04,130 --> 00:13:06,880
I'll give it to you cheap, so buy some.

122
00:13:06,882 --> 00:13:08,520
You hear that?

123
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:13,721
Why don't you set today's dinner table with this webfoot octopus in season?

124
00:13:13,721 --> 00:13:18,013
This is the Saeuh Island and I'm reporter Joh Bo Ram.

125
00:13:32,464 --> 00:13:36,468
I'm going to see dad. Will you go with me?

126
00:13:36,468 --> 00:13:38,869
I'm not going.

127
00:13:38,869 --> 00:13:40,905
Joon Pyo...

128
00:13:54,868 --> 00:13:56,788
Joon Pyo.

129
00:13:58,361 --> 00:14:00,693
Come talk with Mom.

130
00:14:04,329 --> 00:14:06,097
Mom?

131
00:14:13,882 --> 00:14:16,220
Do you really think

132
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:19,770
that you were even once my mom?

133
00:14:26,918 --> 00:14:31,040
Why don't you quit with the act of being a mother when it doesn't suit you,

134
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,850
Chairwoman Kang.

135
00:14:55,848 --> 00:14:57,145
There's no reason for me to go.
What?

136
00:14:57,145 --> 00:14:58,750
What?

137
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:01,180
If you're going to go, go by yourself.

138
00:15:01,180 --> 00:15:02,321
Goo Joon Pyo...

139
00:15:02,321 --> 00:15:04,210
Joon Pyo, are you serious?

140
00:15:04,210 --> 00:15:07,020
Don't be like this. Go and see her once.

141
00:15:12,932 --> 00:15:15,433
I said I'm not interested!

142
00:15:20,751 --> 00:15:22,941
I'll ask you one more time.

143
00:15:22,941 --> 00:15:24,842
Are you sure?

144
00:15:27,163 --> 00:15:29,848
Are you sure?
If you miss her so much, you go.

145
00:15:31,544 --> 00:15:33,210
Then I'm going first.

146
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:36,320
Whether you go or not, do whatever you want.

147
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:52,800
[Incheon City]

148
00:16:07,249 --> 00:16:10,989
When times are like this, don't you need Geum Jan Di the most?

149
00:16:11,733 --> 00:16:14,259
What can I do by bringing her back here?

150
00:16:16,930 --> 00:16:19,970
There is nothing that I can promise her...

151
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:22,730
Promising her that I'd always make her laugh,

152
00:16:24,119 --> 00:16:27,907
that I'd always make her happy, so just trust in me... I've lost the confidence to keep those kinds of promises.

153
00:16:27,907 --> 00:16:28,988
Joon Pyo.

154
00:16:28,988 --> 00:16:32,077
The fact that I am the son of that kind of person.

155
00:16:33,078 --> 00:16:35,847
The fact that I am a member of that kind of family.

156
00:16:36,898 --> 00:16:39,220
Even I hate it.

157
00:16:39,220 --> 00:16:41,150
So how do you think she feels?

158
00:16:43,303 --> 00:16:47,026
With all that she's had to endure already, I'm sure she really hates it.

159
00:16:47,026 --> 00:16:49,294
It's Geum Jan Di, so the situation can be different.

160
00:16:49,294 --> 00:16:51,296
That's even more of a reason not to.

161
00:16:52,875 --> 00:16:55,500
Because it's the woman that I love.

162
00:16:56,850 --> 00:16:59,170
That's why it's not going to happen even more now.

163
00:17:10,683 --> 00:17:13,652
It would have been nice if we sold the rest of that.

164
00:17:13,652 --> 00:17:15,500
Mom, I'm hungry!

165
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,540
I'm sorry, San. I will have it ready soon.

166
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:20,430
Let's go.

167
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:22,630
I should cook some stew.

168
00:17:24,797 --> 00:17:26,932
What's going on?

169
00:17:26,932 --> 00:17:30,735
What's going on? That's what we want to ask you.

170
00:17:30,735 --> 00:17:33,850
There's a limit to your thinking of what dumb country folks we are!

171
00:17:33,850 --> 00:17:36,870
What kind of scam are you trying to pull?

172
00:17:36,870 --> 00:17:38,044
A scam?

173
00:17:38,044 --> 00:17:39,815
You said you were the future daughter-in-law of Shinhwa Group!

174
00:17:39,815 --> 00:17:43,226
My daughter says that there is someone else who is the future daughter-in-law.

175
00:17:43,226 --> 00:17:48,120
See this? This lady is the heiress to a group much bigger than Shinhwa!

176
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:51,089
The fact that they were going to get married was even on the news!

177
00:17:51,089 --> 00:17:53,058
That's old news.

178
00:17:53,058 --> 00:17:54,470
What?

179
00:17:54,470 --> 00:18:00,630
So you mean you're really the future daughter-in-law of Shinhwa?

180
00:18:01,139 --> 00:18:02,601
Well, that's not quite it either.

181
00:18:02,601 --> 00:18:05,671
We don't care! Just give us back the money that you borrowed right now!!

182
00:18:05,671 --> 00:18:07,673
What? Right now?

183
00:18:07,673 --> 00:18:10,709
Yes! You never know, you might just run away in the middle of the night tonight!

184
00:18:10,709 --> 00:18:12,006
That's right!

185
00:18:12,006 --> 00:18:14,610
Look at what you've already just sat around and received!

186
00:18:14,610 --> 00:18:17,910
There's no difference between that and scamming us!

187
00:18:17,910 --> 00:18:21,352
Pay us even the interest right now!!!

188
00:18:21,352 --> 00:18:23,300
Why all of a sudden?

189
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:25,600
Give it back!

190
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:30,260
Give it all back!

191
00:18:30,260 --> 00:18:32,740
You should pay us back.

192
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:35,720
No, wait...

193
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:38,369
I'll pay it.

194
00:18:39,586 --> 00:18:40,940
Sunbae.

195
00:18:40,940 --> 00:18:43,675
Oh... that... that... master is...

196
00:18:43,675 --> 00:18:45,340
That money.

197
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:48,060
I'll repay it.

198
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:49,810
Oh gosh.

199
00:18:55,870 --> 00:18:58,090
He must be from a rich family.

200
00:19:00,391 --> 00:19:03,194
What should we do?

201
00:19:03,194 --> 00:19:05,331
Did you see that, see that?

202
00:19:07,868 --> 00:19:11,070
I guess it was true that she had a rich future son-in-law!

203
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:14,205
So is he the heir of Shinhwa Group?

204
00:19:14,205 --> 00:19:17,143
Oh, just look at his face! He had a sense of nobility flowing out of him!

205
00:19:17,143 --> 00:19:20,413
Oh, my. I've never seen such a handsome Young Master.

206
00:19:20,413 --> 00:19:22,604
I envy them.

207
00:19:31,408 --> 00:19:35,893
I'm not going to die alone. I'm not going to die alone!

208
00:19:53,657 --> 00:19:57,915
How did you know that I was here?

209
00:19:57,915 --> 00:19:59,851
I heard it.

210
00:20:02,616 --> 00:20:04,489
The emergency bell.

211
00:20:06,823 --> 00:20:10,194
I tossed and turned every night, afraid that I wouldn't be able to hear it.

212
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:15,070
♫ Because I long for you ♫

213
00:20:15,803 --> 00:20:18,207
How can this happen?

214
00:20:19,731 --> 00:20:23,340
How can a person do such a thing?

215
00:20:27,268 --> 00:20:31,442
I... have received so much from you, Sunbae.

216
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:37,910
♫ I'll only look at you ♫

217
00:20:37,910 --> 00:20:41,970
♫ Can I go back to before ♫

218
00:20:41,970 --> 00:20:44,699
But you have given me more.

219
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:53,470
♫ when I didn't even know your name ♫

220
00:20:53,470 --> 00:21:02,520
♫ Just a little longer, I'll only look at you ♫

221
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:07,470
♫ I can see no one but you ♫

222
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:12,580
♫ I promise ♫

223
00:21:30,283 --> 00:21:33,639
How is Grandpa doing?

224
00:21:33,639 --> 00:21:36,420
As usual he's attending to work

225
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:40,370
and will probably continue until he collapses again.

226
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:43,941
That is so like him.

227
00:21:46,060 --> 00:21:53,500
♫ I tried to erase the stained memories ♫

228
00:21:55,410 --> 00:22:00,390
♫ but they keep spreading ♫

229
00:22:00,390 --> 00:22:03,158
Grandpa gave me this.

230
00:22:03,158 --> 00:22:06,136
It was what my Grandma gave my mother.

231
00:22:07,944 --> 00:22:09,746
Sunbae.

232
00:22:10,844 --> 00:22:13,486
I don't know when I started to feel like this,

233
00:22:13,486 --> 00:22:15,175
but...

234
00:22:15,885 --> 00:22:18,253
I cannot live without you.

235
00:22:20,490 --> 00:22:25,860
♫ I love you, I never said it ♫

236
00:22:25,860 --> 00:22:30,750
♫ I had to keep it inside and erase it ♫

237
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:36,890
♫ Like this, living without you ♫

238
00:22:38,206 --> 00:22:40,404
I cannot accept this.

239
00:22:47,384 --> 00:22:49,322
Jan Di.

240
00:22:49,322 --> 00:22:51,968
I told myself that I can forget it.

241
00:22:54,995 --> 00:22:57,816
I thought that I had forgotten it all.

242
00:22:59,702 --> 00:23:01,812
However...

243
00:23:03,733 --> 00:23:05,434
However...

244
00:23:13,324 --> 00:23:16,619
I can't seem to be able to throw this away.

245
00:23:19,206 --> 00:23:21,626
I just can't seem to let it go.

246
00:23:23,599 --> 00:23:26,663
I can't separate Goo Joon Pyo from me.

247
00:23:33,410 --> 00:23:35,632
I'm sorry.

248
00:23:36,947 --> 00:23:39,346
I'm sorry, Sunbae.

249
00:23:41,406 --> 00:23:43,129
It's ok.

250
00:23:49,392 --> 00:23:51,031
It's ok.

251
00:24:18,020 --> 00:24:21,950
♫ No words in this world could possibly describe ♫

252
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:23,960
Jan Di...

253
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:27,110
I can't give her up.

254
00:24:29,222 --> 00:24:31,882
Even though I always make things hard for her.

255
00:24:32,719 --> 00:24:36,471
I've sometimes thought it might be better to let her go to you.

256
00:24:37,168 --> 00:24:38,739
No...

257
00:24:40,138 --> 00:24:43,276
If I had to give Jan Di to another guy,

258
00:24:44,692 --> 00:24:48,031
I don't even want to think about it. But if I had to,

259
00:24:50,530 --> 00:24:53,695
I thought you should be the one.

260
00:24:55,027 --> 00:24:57,430
It can't be anyone else but you, Ji Hoo.

261
00:24:58,136 --> 00:25:00,407
