522
00:55:29,424 --> 00:55:32,488
That's really funny, Oppa.

523
00:55:33,673 --> 00:55:35,036
Joon Pyo.

524
00:55:35,036 --> 00:55:37,529
Ji Hoo. You were there?

525
00:55:37,529 --> 00:55:39,724
Jan Di unnie.

526
00:55:41,306 --> 00:55:42,998
Hello.

527
00:55:42,998 --> 00:55:45,329
Unnie, did you see Joon Pyo oppa's crutches?

528
00:55:45,329 --> 00:55:47,580
They're titanium. Pretty funny, huh?

529
00:55:47,580 --> 00:55:50,250
It's not like he's Iron Man or anything.

530
00:55:52,489 --> 00:55:56,359
Jan Di unnie's friend is so handsome.

531
00:55:59,970 --> 00:56:04,514
Hello. I'm Jang Yoo Mi. Nice to meet you.

532
00:56:09,035 --> 00:56:12,329
It's cold. Let's go back inside.

533
00:56:30,520 --> 00:56:36,040
Actual purchasing power is shown...

534
00:56:43,020 --> 00:56:44,695
Who is it?

535
00:56:52,219 --> 00:56:54,660
I have brought pizza.

536
00:56:58,079 --> 00:57:01,501
It would be so great if I could see it through a telescope or something.

537
00:57:01,501 --> 00:57:03,612
Oppa, do you like stars?

538
00:57:05,932 --> 00:57:07,366
Stars?

539
00:57:08,747 --> 00:57:12,176
The brightest star in winter...

540
00:57:12,176 --> 00:57:16,116
In other words, like Goo Joon Pyo.

541
00:57:16,116 --> 00:57:21,040
Then, I am this star.

542
00:57:21,040 --> 00:57:22,900
This one.

543
00:57:28,381 --> 00:57:31,315
Oppa. What's wrong? Are you hurting somewhere?

544
00:57:31,315 --> 00:57:36,714
There's something important that I seem to have forgotten.

545
00:57:38,252 --> 00:57:40,267
I can't remember it.

546
00:57:41,260 --> 00:57:43,998
My chest feels so tight that I feel like I'm going to burst.

547
00:57:44,782 --> 00:57:46,362
Don't stress too much over it.

548
00:57:46,362 --> 00:57:49,872
If it's important, it will come back eventually.

549
00:57:49,872 --> 00:57:53,955
If it doesn't come back, doesn't it mean that it wasn't really that important to begin with?

550
00:57:53,955 --> 00:57:57,233
If you keep stressing about it, it won't be good for you physically.

551
00:58:03,869 --> 00:58:06,876
Yo... What's up? Are you okay?

552
00:58:06,876 --> 00:58:08,301
Hello.

553
00:58:08,301 --> 00:58:09,577
We meet again.

554
00:58:09,577 --> 00:58:11,275
We are H.C.

555
00:58:11,275 --> 00:58:12,711
H.C.?

556
00:58:12,711 --> 00:58:14,205
Hospital couple.

557
00:58:14,205 --> 00:58:19,080
All the patients and the nurses basically gave us that official title.

558
00:58:19,080 --> 00:58:21,823
What do you think? Do we suit each other?

559
00:58:21,823 --> 00:58:26,006
Joon Pyo, do you still not remember anything?

560
00:58:26,006 --> 00:58:28,378
What exactly am I supposed to remember?

561
00:58:28,378 --> 00:58:31,434
Geum Jan Di. You don't remember?

562
00:58:31,434 --> 00:58:34,066
Why do you keep talking about Jan Di or something?!

563
00:58:34,066 --> 00:58:37,687
I mean, why should I remember your girl?

564
00:58:37,687 --> 00:58:39,423
Oh, forget it!

565
00:58:39,423 --> 00:58:42,426
I don't know where you met this girl, so unsophisticated.

566
00:58:42,426 --> 00:58:45,061
What does she think she is, a gang member or something?

567
00:58:45,061 --> 00:58:46,964
Just make sure she doesn't come in and out of my hospital room.

568
00:58:46,964 --> 00:58:49,103
Goo Joon Pyo!

569
00:58:50,334 --> 00:58:52,435
Please stop.

570
00:59:13,090 --> 00:59:15,124
What is wrong with him?

571
00:59:37,915 --> 00:59:39,849
Sunbae.

572
00:59:51,862 --> 00:59:53,963
I'll bring tea.

573
00:59:55,532 --> 00:59:57,266
I'm sorry.

574
01:00:02,672 --> 01:00:05,375
Why should you be sorry?

575
01:00:05,375 --> 01:00:07,977
I'm the one who is sorry.

576
01:00:07,977 --> 01:00:10,680
I got so mad without even my knowing.

577
01:00:13,718 --> 01:00:17,011
I didn't stop you because I thought Joon Pyo would be hurt.

578
01:00:17,011 --> 01:00:21,173
If you hit him, I thought you would be hurt more, emotionally.

579
01:00:21,173 --> 01:00:23,837
That's why I stopped you.

580
01:00:29,024 --> 01:00:31,378
How long did you wait outside?

581
01:00:31,378 --> 01:00:33,794
Why are your hands so cold?

582
01:00:37,164 --> 01:00:39,218
Let me see.

583
01:00:44,971 --> 01:00:48,969
The one that's cold is your heart.

584
01:00:51,196 --> 01:00:54,431
You don't have to pretend to be strong in front of me.

585
01:00:59,220 --> 01:01:02,058
I'm not pretending to be strong.

586
01:01:03,423 --> 01:01:05,837
It's because you're here.

587
01:01:06,575 --> 01:01:10,213
You being here gives me strength.

588
01:01:14,660 --> 01:01:16,748
I'll go make tea.

589
01:01:43,950 --> 01:01:48,470
♫ Although I ask it to stop, to stop wherever it is ♫

590
01:01:48,470 --> 01:01:52,930
♫ My heart keeps going to you ♫

591
01:01:52,930 --> 01:01:57,420
♫ You don't even listen, or give in ♫

592
01:01:57,420 --> 01:02:01,780
♫ Why is my love like this? ♫

593
01:02:01,780 --> 01:02:05,430
♫ Counting each memory one by one ♫

594
01:02:05,430 --> 01:02:11,619
Abracadabra, Goo Joon Pyo, remember Geum Jan Di.

595
01:02:11,619 --> 01:02:13,269
I remember.

596
01:02:13,269 --> 01:02:15,980
The thing I forgot is...

597
01:02:15,980 --> 01:02:17,860
you, right?

598
01:02:17,860 --> 01:02:20,000
It's all over now.

599
01:02:20,000 --> 01:02:24,177
That in this ridiculous way, you guys are ending?

600
01:02:24,177 --> 01:02:25,249
I can't go along with it.

601
01:02:25,249 --> 01:02:29,370
That girl's facial expression... I can't seem to erase...

602
01:02:29,370 --> 01:02:33,898
In the end... Geum Jan Di and Goo Joon Pyo...

603
01:02:35,443 --> 01:02:37,258
only amounted to this.

604
01:02:37,258 --> 01:02:40,136
This is all it amounted to.

605
01:02:43,279 --> 01:02:48,247
We have gathered you all here to announce something special.

606
01:02:48,247 --> 01:02:55,513
Goo Joon Pyo and Jang Yoo Mi, have decided to go study in the US next month.

607
01:03:00,040 --> 01:03:04,620
♫ No matter how much I strech my hands out, how much I call you ♫

608
01:03:04,620 --> 01:03:09,200
♫ You are only far away from me ♫

609
01:03:09,200 --> 01:03:13,660
♫ This love will only become a painful wound ♫

610
01:03:13,660 --> 01:03:18,030
♫ Why can't I just erase it? ♫

611
01:03:18,030 --> 01:03:22,610
♫ Something must have happened to my heart ♫

612
01:03:22,610 --> 01:03:27,070
♫ I must have become a fool blinded by love ♫

613
01:03:27,070 --> 01:03:31,610
♫ Just one place, everyday one place ♫

614
01:03:31,610 --> 01:03:36,100
♫ Looking at the sad light called you ♫

